            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Trimmy 0.9.0</h2>
<ul>
<li>Claude Code: add optional prompt-decoration flattening for copied slash commands while preserving ordinary wrapped prose (#19, thanks @evoleinik).</li>
<li>Settings: add an option to hide the menu bar icon while keeping Trimmy running (#24, thanks @qazi0).</li>
<li>Text cleanup: dedent copied prose where most paragraph lines share the same leading whitespace (#10, thanks @arunsathiya).</li>
<li>Website: add a copy button for the Homebrew install command.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/steipete/Trimmy/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">View full changelog</a></p>
]]></description>
